## 13. Final Note

The application should not be treated as a set of independent screens. It is a workflow-driven system whose reliability, commercial performance, and member value all depend on the integrity of the workflows defined above.

If any major workflow family is omitted, the product may still launch, but it will not operate effectively at scale.

